35:59.070 --> 36:02.039
Then that's precisely why it looks like one.

36:03.875 --> 36:05.604
Let's go.

36:25.296 --> 36:29.824
This is the most beautiful thing l've ever seen.

36:31.669 --> 36:33.762
Let's go.

36:47.485 --> 36:51.649
Look, baby, look. lt comes with free nuns.

37:11.943 --> 37:13.968
- Vous êtes Américains?
- Oui.

37:14.045 --> 37:17.173
Welcome to Hôtel des Rêves.
l am Henri Margeaux.

37:17.282 --> 37:19.682
Nous sommes Sarah et Tom Leezak.

37:19.784 --> 37:21.149
- Leezak, no!
- Oui.

37:21.219 --> 37:23.119
- The honeymooners?
- Oui.

37:23.187 --> 37:25.951
- No!
- Oui. Why?

37:26.024 --> 37:29.790
