38:28.219 --> 38:30.016
Right. Sorry.

38:32.790 --> 38:37.955
Now fight your deep urge to be cheap,
and give the bellboy a large tip.

38:38.062 --> 38:39.222
All right.

38:39.297 --> 38:43.859
- Hey, do you guys provide satellite TV?
- TV in bar.

