he wouldn't be concerned with TV.

39:20.004 --> 39:21.494
He makes a point.

39:21.606 --> 39:26.134
- l gotta call Mom and Dad.
- Talk about killing the romance.

39:26.244 --> 39:29.145
l told them l'd call. lt'll just take a minute.

39:31.082 --> 39:33.482
Hi, Mom? lt's Peewee.

39:33.584 --> 39:35.415
Say hi to Pussy for me.

39:39.323 --> 39:41.052
Tom says hello.

39:41.492 --> 39:44.086
Yeah. Oh, it's so great.

39:46.864 --> 39:52.166
''To Tom and Sarah.
Enhance thy honeymoon. Love, Kyle.''

39:52.770 --> 39:54.829
l'll call you later, Mom. Bye.

39:56.207 --> 39:59.438
Cheese and rice.
ls that a Thunderstick A200?

39:59.510 --> 40:01.375
Since when did you become an expert?

40:01.479 --> 40:05.711
- l told you about that night l had in college.
- Not about the hardware.

40:05.817 --> 40:08.047
Getting a visual?

40:09.487 --> 40:11.955
We gotta charge this thing.

40:19.831 --> 40:24.291
- That plug won't fit in a European outlet.
