40:27.472 --> 40:28.666
Come on.

40:28.740 --> 40:29.798
Don't force it.

40:42.220 --> 40:44.085
Are you OK? Are you OK?

40:44.188 --> 40:48.921
Holy dude Jesus. Good thing that
didn't happen when we were using it.

40:51.329 --> 40:52.421
Oh, God.

40:52.530 --> 40:55.931
Allez dans la cour,
s'il vous plaît, tout de suite.

40:56.033 --> 40:58.399
Come on! Come on, Thunderstick!

40:58.503 --> 41:02.098
- Oh, no. OK, just leave it.
- Let's go, let's go, let's go.

41:29.200 --> 41:33.796
My grandparents
installed the wiring in the hotel

41:33.905 --> 41:36.635
before World War First!

41:38.609 --> 41:44.605
