to bring out your toys and ignore the sign!

41:50.154 --> 41:52.782
That is the...

41:52.890 --> 41:56.917
- That's in French, for chrissakes.
- That's because we're in France.

41:56.994 --> 42:00.293
- ls there anything we could do?
- Pay the damages.

42:00.398 --> 42:01.763
Hold on there, Jacques.

42:01.833 --> 42:04.734
Je m'appelle Henri Margeaux.

42:04.802 --> 42:09.136
Whatever! Look, this hotel gets
guests from all over the world.

42:09.240 --> 42:12.232
lt's your responsibility
to put American on your signs.

42:12.310 --> 42:13.641
He means English.

42:13.744 --> 42:16.338
l'm trying to negotiate.

42:16.447 --> 42:18.642
So l must make my hotel of dreams

42:18.749 --> 42:21.775
like every Howard Johnson's,
with a bright orange roof?

42:21.853 --> 42:25.186
- lt wouldn't hurt.
- lmbécile de cochon d'Américain.

42:25.289 --> 42:28.486
- Cochon what?
- Stupid American pig.

42:32.530 --> 42:38.162
Well, l guess that makes you
a stupid French frog!

42:38.269 --> 42:40.294
Oh, yeah. l said it. Frog!

42:40.371 --> 42:42.635
Get out of my Hôtel des Rêves!

42:42.707 --> 42:46.143
l wouldn't stay in this dump if you paid us!

42:47.011 --> 42:49.878
- Let's go to the Ho Jo's.
- There are no Ho Jo's here.

42:49.981 --> 42:51.710
Sarah, please!

42:51.816 --> 42:56.116
There is a farm up the road.
And they have a nice pigsty for you!

42:56.187 --> 42:59.384
Yeah? Maybe they'll have
a nice little bulldozer,

42:59.490 --> 43:02.721
and we can finish this place off, tough guy!

43:02.827 --> 43:06.319
And the credit bill will be
a fat one, Mr Tough Guy!

43:06.397 --> 43:11.027
Yeah? Well, we're keeping the champagne
and the cheese, Jacques-strap!

43:12.737 --> 43:14.364
Let's go, honey.

43:16.173 --> 43:18.232
What's wrong?

43:19.310 --> 43:22.040
Where are we gonna stay, Tom?

43:22.146 --> 43:25.673
Don't worry. This is a vacation zone.
We'll find a place.

43:25.750 --> 43:27.718
Now get your shit. Let's go.

43:28.819 --> 43:30.719
What's the next place?

43:30.821 --> 43:36.851
The next hotel with no vacancy
would be Schloss Hilliger Winterswald.

43:36.928 --> 43:39.897
- How far is it?
- 120 kilometers.

43:39.997 --> 43:41.931
ln miles, please!

43:42.033 --> 43:45.059
74.4. You multiply by 0.6.

43:45.169 --> 43:49.071
- l'm learning so much.
- Oh, me too. Me too.

43:56.013 --> 43:57.605
Let me guess...

44:04.388 --> 44:06.948
This is great. This is just what we need.

44:07.058 --> 44:10.892
- Do you want me to drive?
- Honey, l can drive in the snow.

44:13.631 --> 44:15.929
Turn off your brights, jackass!

44:48.099 --> 44:52.263
Great. Now we get to freeze to death.

44:55.106 --> 45:00.601
Look, we'll just... We'll sleep in here
and we'll dig out in the morning.

45:00.678 --> 45:04.671
l'm so glad l get to hear the phrase
''We'll dig out'' on my honeymoon.

45:10.021 --> 45:12.489
Just get it over with now and blame me.

45:12.590 --> 45:17.584
lf you hadn't insulted Henri, we wouldn't
be spending the evening in a snowball.

45:17.661 --> 45:23.258
l'm sorry. Next time, l'll try to be a little
bit more refined like your friend Peter.

45:23.334 --> 45:26.132
- Good night, Tom.
- Good night, Sarah.

46:02.173 --> 46:04.368
Are you gonna hate me for ever?

46:07.078 --> 46:09.376
l don't know.

46:13.350 --> 46:15.011
Wanna get drunk and make out?

46:15.086 --> 46:18.886
Well, that's not gonna get me drunk,
but we could make out.

46:24.228 --> 46:27.322
We could get injured doing this.

46:27.398 --> 46:31.027
l'll settle for a cuddle.
Just let me get the shifter out of my ass.

46:42.079 --> 46:45.173
Sarah... lt's morning.

47:04.902 --> 47:07.097
Oh, my God.

47:10.741 --> 47:12.868
- Oh, my...
- Oh, my God.

47:12.943 --> 47:14.774
lt's incredible.

47:15.212 --> 47:19.706
- Let's just stay here for the rest of the trip.
- Fine with me.

47:26.991 --> 47:29.118
- Hey! Help!
- Excuse me!

47:33.497 --> 47:36.091
Blue car, blue car!

47:37.168 --> 47:38.066
lt worked.

48:10.267 --> 48:14.101
We can catch the two o'clock train to Venice
and go straight to the Gianna.

48:14.171 --> 48:18.198
- Our reservation isn't until Tuesday.
- So we'll stay a few extra days.

48:18.309 --> 48:20.675
l just put a castle on my credit card.

48:20.778 --> 48:24.043
We can't afford to stay at the Gianna
for a few extra days.

48:24.148 --> 48:27.140
So l'll call my dad up,
and he'll lend us the money.

48:27.218 --> 48:30.517
No, there's no way
l'm taking money from your dad.

48:30.621 --> 48:32.987
Pride is the crutch of the insecure.

48:33.057 --> 48:35.890
You are not taking the money.
l am taking the money.

48:35.993 --> 48:40.191
No, we don't need to take the money.
This is about us now.

48:40.297 --> 48:44.063
My dad told me about this
nice little pensione in Venice...

48:44.168 --> 48:45.396
Pensione?

48:45.502 --> 48:48.630
- GroBes ScheiBhaus.
- Excuse me.

48:48.706 --> 48:50.674
Could you just drive?

48:50.741 --> 48:52.402
Please just let me call my dad.

48:52.509 --> 48:55.740
No! This is our honeymoon, not his.

48:55.846 --> 48:59.543
So it's fine to stay at a pensione
that your father recommended?

48:59.650 --> 49:03.586
We're staying at the Pensione Funicello,
and we'll have a good time.

49:03.687 --> 49:07.885
l can't take this any more! Honeymoons
are supposed to be all champagne

49:07.992 --> 49:11.758
and room service and lovemaking!
We haven't made love!

49:11.862 --> 49:14.922
No. What do we get?
We get evicted from a five-star hotel

49:15.032 --> 49:18.900
