49:34.084 --> 49:37.884
eat pasta, gaze out at the Piazza del...

49:39.123 --> 49:41.216
something-something.

49:42.126 --> 49:43.559
lt's gonna be heaven.

49:54.204 --> 49:56.570
Pensione Funicello?

50:00.978 --> 50:03.310
Are you sure?

50:05.616 --> 50:07.413
How bad could it be?

50:11.255 --> 50:13.120
Aw, crap.

50:20.631 --> 50:22.895
We're in this together, right?

50:25.069 --> 50:28.766
Do you have four men staring
at your boobies right now?

50:34.478 --> 50:35.911
No.

51:12.516 --> 51:14.347
Yeah, just...

51:14.451 --> 51:18.114
You know, we'll try it for one night,
and if we don't...

51:18.188 --> 51:20.452
Live.

51:20.524 --> 51:26.121
..like it, we'll, you know,
go somewhere nicer tomorrow.

51:35.739 --> 51:38.469
This is actually happening!

51:43.213 --> 51:46.205
We're never gonna forget this honeymoon.

52:17.848 --> 52:19.543
Sorry.

52:44.708 --> 52:47.268
We can show those paisanos how it's done.

52:52.082 --> 52:54.778
Cockroach, cockroach, cockroach!

52:54.885 --> 52:57.376
Oh, honey! Honey, honey! l'll get him!

52:59.656 --> 53:02.716
Let's get outta here, please!

53:02.793 --> 53:05.284
- We're checking out!
- l don't wanna touch it!

53:05.395 --> 53:07.260
Get it off me!

53:11.568 --> 53:13.798
Thanks for the help, Daddy.

53:14.938 --> 53:17.930
l miss you.

53:20.077 --> 53:21.942
Honey, he wants to talk to you.

53:22.012 --> 53:26.574
