53:35.792 --> 53:37.783
Hello there, Mr McNerney.

53:37.861 --> 53:41.797
Please bear in mind that
our daughter loves him, Dan.

53:41.865 --> 53:48.100
Listen, Leezak, l don't expect
a cracker like you to ever measure up

53:48.171 --> 53:52.005
