a good match for my daughter.

53:52.109 --> 53:53.940
But l'll tell you what l do expect.

53:54.011 --> 53:58.641
l expect you to pay me back in full just as
soon as that silly-ass radio show of yours

53:58.715 --> 54:00.945
yields any kind of reasonable income.

54:01.018 --> 54:03.316
Goodbye, cracker.

54:05.222 --> 54:07.486
Ass-bag!

54:07.558 --> 54:10.220
- What was that?
- He called me a cracker!

54:10.327 --> 54:12.557
A cracker, honey!

54:12.663 --> 54:14.722
He did not.

54:14.831 --> 54:19.131
