''Well, wonderful, wonderful.''

54:19.202 --> 54:22.865
He's got your whole family
praying that this marriage fails.

54:22.973 --> 54:25.533
Mom's never said a bad word about you.

54:25.642 --> 54:30.136
Wow, Pussy's never insulted me!
Now l feel loved.

54:30.213 --> 54:32.704
Like your father's neverjudged me?

54:32.816 --> 54:35.910
No, he hasn't. Not once.

54:42.492 --> 54:44.255
Maybe we should just have sex.

54:44.361 --> 54:48.058
Call me crazy, but l'm just
not in the mood to make love.

54:50.367 --> 54:55.168
l'm not, either. But we haven't had sex once
since we've been married,

54:55.238 --> 54:58.435
and there is something
very, very wrong with that.

54:58.542 --> 55:01.568
And l have to tell you... lt's not funny!

55:01.678 --> 55:04.010
l'm sorry.

55:04.081 --> 55:06.413
l'm concerned.

55:06.516 --> 55:12.512
Let's go to sleep. We'll get a good rest,
we'll sightsee tomorrow.

55:12.589 --> 55:14.682
Be fresh in the morning.

55:16.393 --> 55:18.020
Fine.

55:19.630 --> 55:22.030
And then we'll have sex.

56:14.818 --> 56:19.118
lmagine Ernest Hemingway sitting
right over there at the Caffè Florian,

56:19.189 --> 56:23.956
