History doesn't interest you at all, does it?

56:34.171 --> 56:39.438
Huh? Yeah, it does. l wasn't an art history
major, though, so it's not like...

56:39.509 --> 56:43.104
You don't have to be an art history major
to appreciate art.

56:43.180 --> 56:46.013
- Whoa, whoa.
- What? What?

56:46.116 --> 56:48.277
Do you hear that?

56:48.351 --> 56:52.117
The bells? No? What is it, honey?

56:52.189 --> 56:54.282
What?

56:55.058 --> 56:56.855
What?

56:56.960 --> 56:58.154
What?

56:58.228 --> 57:01.459
What are we listening to?

57:02.833 --> 57:05.324
What? What is it? l can help.

57:05.402 --> 57:08.667
- lt's a message from God. lt's a mes...
- God?

57:10.307 --> 57:12.867
There's a ground ball...

57:12.976 --> 57:14.841
Jackpot!

57:16.747 --> 57:19.477
Honey, we still have to see the Tintorettos.

57:21.485 --> 57:26.718
Oh, the church art is unbelievable,

57:26.823 --> 57:29.383
but it all kinda looks the same to me.

57:31.027 --> 57:33.825
You know l love sports.

